\"to\": 934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the eventing seminar, FEI eventing committee chairman and Olympic gold medallist David O'Connor stressed that the \\\"short-format\\\" cross-country would still run according to the current specifications of 10 minutes.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 972, \"end\": 975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1015871333069399e-33, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1031, \"end\": 1045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_O'Connor_(equestrian)\", \"score\": 0.47900860568712494, \"rank\": 0.5000000000000275, \"text\": \"David O'Connor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_O'Connor_(equestrian)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_O'Connor_(equestrian)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eventing seminar\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"short-format\\\" cross-country\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"the current specifications\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"10 minutes\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An FEI spokesman toldH&Htoday that the FEI board held a teleconference on Tuesday, adding: \\\"The board agreed with the proposed modifications to the eventing Olympic competition format, which will be shared with the IOC by the set deadline of 1 March 2024 as per the official international federations consultation process launched by the IOC.\\\"\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1170, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1015871333069399e-33, \"t